```plantuml
@startuml blockchain-signaling-system_bloss-core
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

actor "Network Administrator" as Admin

rectangle "BloSS" {
  rectangle "REST API" as BlossAPI
  rectangle "Manager" as BlossManager
}

rectangle "Stalk" {
  rectangle "Ryu Controller" as RyuController
  rectangle "REST API" as StalkAPI
  rectangle "Flow Statistics Manager" as FlowStatsManager
}

rectangle "Pollen" {
  rectangle "Blockchain Interaction" as Blockchain
  rectangle "Data Storage" as DataStorage
  rectangle "Attack Reporting" as AttackReporting
}

rectangle "Ethereum Blockchain" as Ethereum
rectangle "InfluxDB" as InfluxDB
rectangle "IPFS" as IPFS

Admin --> BlossAPI : Send attack report
BlossAPI --> RyuController : Request attack detection
RyuController --> FlowStatsManager : Gather flow statistics
FlowStatsManager --> RyuController : Send statistics
RyuController --> BlossManager : Notify potential attacker
BlossManager --> Blockchain : Log attack on blockchain
Blockchain --> Ethereum : Interact with smart contract

BlossAPI --> StalkAPI : Request mitigation
StalkAPI --> RyuController : Block attacker

Blockchain --> DataStorage : Store attack data
DataStorage --> InfluxDB : Store statistics data
DataStorage --> IPFS : Store attack report and keys

Blockchain --> AttackReporting : Process attack report
AttackReporting --> DataStorage : Retrieve report data
@enduml
```